                <h1>How to Quickly Change Dimensions on Canva</h1>
                <p>To change dimensions on Canva, start by selecting your design. Click on the "Resize" button at the top left. Enter your desired width and height, or choose from preset sizes. You can maintain the aspect ratio by checking the box. Hit "Resize" to apply changes or "Copy & resize" to create a new design with the new dimensions.</p>
